weasel_1's LJ New Year Party (Now At Least 8% Politically Correct!)

Started : 01st January 2006 06:56:22 AM
Ended : 01st January 2006 03:37:37 PM		 Alco Money! : $ 542

Guests of Honour

of_old_dresses is an up-tight Fundementalist Christian and a prolific barfer, particularly at parties such as this who would sell their soul for one night of passion with Hitler. of_old_dresses decided to not drink because of their religious beliefs.
winterlion is a fanciful Agnostic and a rather poor excuse for a drinker. winterlion drank 7 Lagers, 4 Bloody Marys, 3 Cosmopolitans, 2 Pulques.
wassomeoneelse is a sprightly Agnostic and an ardent supporter of the 'Givuz a new Liver for Free' campaign. wassomeoneelse drank 5 Hot Toddys, 7 Mint Juleps, 1 Pulque, 1 Mescal, 1 White Wine, 3 Gins, 1 Sambucca, 1 Whiskey.
rev3 is an erratic Buddhist and a serious booze-hound. rev3 drank 11 Whiskeys, 8 Ales.
cute_and_fuzzy is an easy-going Agnostic. cute_and_fuzzy drank 11 Pulques, 4 Vodkas, 2 Poteens, 1 White Wine.
soberrover is a bewildered Taoist and is usually the last person standing at the bar. soberrover drank 1 Champagne.
chef_socrates is an insane Atheist. chef_socrates drank 7 Rums, 1 Cider, 3 Kahluas, 2 Vodkas.
missjenn85 is a bouncy Hindu and a full-time waster who spends most of their salary on alcohol. missjenn85 drank 1 Gin, 9 Bloody Marys.
mspixiegirl is a hearty Agnostic. mspixiegirl drank 5 Aftershocks, 9 Sherrys, 1 Poteen, 1 Pernod, 1 Cosmopolitan.
afro_san is an upbeat Hindu. afro_san drank 11 Gins, 2 Absinthes, 2 White Wines, 2 Vermouths, 1 Lager.
weasel_1 is a disconsolate Liberal Christian and an all around space cadet who's mind has been destroyed by beer over the years. weasel_1 decided to not drink because of their religious beliefs.

Sick!

weasel_1's home is completely covered in vomit and it'll definitely take more than a 7 man operation to clean it up!

Fights

of_old_dresses is currently sueing chef_socrates for $1,000,000 after the Atheist reportedly shouted 'of_old_dresses! Your God reeks of shit! Your Church reeks of shit! You reek of shit! You are full of shit!'.

Lovers

No one would have predicted it at the start of the evening but it seems like weasel_1 has found an eternal soulmate in mspixiegirl. Oh the romance!

The Drunkest

In the middle of the night rev3 woke up shouting "DRINK!!! FECK!!! ARSE!!! seemingly at noone.

Random Events

soberrover bored everyone with fascinating stories about their collection of exotic french ticklers.

winterlion's irrational fear of toasters stems from an incident where their father jammed his manly adapter in the bread slot. Being an evil bastard afro_san chased winterlion around the house with one all night!

winterlion and chef_socrates fought all night after chef_socrates whipped out a picture of winterlion's naked ass and passed it around to alll of the giggling minnions in the room. missjenn85 wet themselves amidst the hysteria.

Salary Raise


I, the Penis, hereby request a raise in salary for the following reasons: 
I do physical labor. 
I work at great depths. 
I plunge head first into everything I do. 
I do not get weekends or public holidays off. 
I work in a damp environment. 
I work in a dark workplace that has poor ventilation. 
I work in high temperatures. 
My work exposes me to contagious diseases. 

Dear Penis, 
After assessing your request, and considering the arguments you 
have raised, the administration rejects your request for the following 
reasons:
You do not work 8 hours straight. You fall asleep after brief work periods. 
You do not always follow the orders of the management team. 
You do not stay in your designated area and are often seen 
visiting other locations. 
You do not take initiative - you need to be pressured and 
stimulated in order to start working. 
You leave the workplace rather messy at the end of your shift. 
You don't always observe necessary safety regulations, such as 
wearing the correct protective clothing. 
You will retire well before you are 65. 
You are unable to work double shifts. 
You sometimes leave your designated work area before you have 
completed the assigned task. 
And if that were not all, you have been seen constantly entering 
and exiting the work place carrying two suspicious-looking bags. 
Sincerely, 
The Management
